
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Parcel Delivered</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #28A745;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 32px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .email-body strong {
      color: #000;
    }

    .parcel-details {
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 24px;
    }

    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #28A745;
      color: #fff;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .email-footer a {
      color: #1E1E1E;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .email-image {
      margin: 32px 0 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-image img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .note-block {
      background: #e8f5e9;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 32px;
      border-left: 5px solid #28A745;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>✅ Parcel Delivered Successfully</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= senderName %></strong>,</p>
      <p>We’re happy to inform you that your parcel has been <strong>delivered</strong> successfully.</p>

      <div class="parcel-details">
        <p><strong>From:</strong> <%= from %></p>
        <p><strong>To:</strong> <%= to %></p>
        <p><strong>Sender Name:</strong> <%= senderName %></p>
        <p><strong>Recipient Name:</strong> <%= recipientName %></p>
        <p><strong>Sender Email:</strong> <%= senderEmail %></p>
        <p><strong>Recipient Email:</strong> <%= recipientEmail %></p>
        <p><strong>Weight:</strong> <%= weight %> kg</p>
        <p><strong>Cost:</strong> $<%= cost %></p>
        <% if (note) { %>
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> <%= note %></p>
        <% } %>

        <div class="status-badge">Delivered</div>
      </div>

      <div class="email-image">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1717495157/hero_r5lgvq.png" alt="Parcel Delivered Image" />
      </div>

      <div class="note-block">
        <p><strong>Need assistance?</strong> If you didn’t expect this delivery or something seems wrong, please contact our support team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>Questions? Reach us at <a href="mailto:excelbdparcel@gmail.com">excelbdparcel@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
